  "prompt": "Which are the least expensive and still good 3D/4D cinema theaters in Delhi NCR?",
  "response": "Finding the least expensive yet good 3D/4D cinema theaters in Delhi NCR can be subjective as prices and experiences can vary. However, some popular and relatively affordable options include:\n\n1. **PVR Cinemas**\n   - PVR Cinemas has multiple locations across Delhi NCR and often provides quality 3D/4D experiences at competitive prices. You can try PVR Anupam Saket, PVR Naraina, or PVR Vikas Puri for relatively lower prices.\n\n2. **Carnival Cinemas**\n   - Carnival Cinemas is another chain that offers good 3D/4D movie experiences at affordable rates. Check locations like Carnival Cinemas Omaxe, Greater Noida for budget-friendly options.\n\n3. **INOX Cinemas**\n   - INOX is known for good quality screens and sound systems. Their prices are generally reasonable, and you can find good 3D experiences at the locations like INOX Nehru Place and INOX Janak Place.\n\n4. **Cinepolis**\n   - Cinepolis offers immersive 4DX experiences in multiple locations such as Cinepolis DLF Place Saket. They are known for their quality screening and might have some affordable options.\n\n5. **SRS Cinemas**\n   - SRS Cinemas in Faridabad is also a good pick for budget-friendly 3D movies. They offer decent facilities and good viewing experiences for comparatively lower prices.\n\nMake sure to look for special discounts, membership offers, and off-peak showtimes to further cut down costs. Additionally, checking online reviews and ratings can help ensure you have a good experience while staying within your budget.",
